pidgin-libnotify
------------------------------------------
This plugin adds a libnotify interface to pidgin, enabling popups much 
like guifications. It has some configuration options, to show popups 
when a buddy signs on, on new messages and on new conversations only.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-50
  libgcc1-4.3.2-2
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.16.3-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.20.4-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.16.3-1
  libintl8-0.17-11
  libnotify1-0.4.5-10
  libpurple0-2.5.8-1
  pidgin-2.5.8-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.63-10
  automake1.9-1.9.6-10
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.9.7-1
  gawk-3.1.6-2
  gcc4-core-4.3.2-2
  gettext-devel-0.17-11
  gnome-common-2.26.0-2
  libtool-2.2.7a-13
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23b-10
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://gaim-libnotify.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/gaim-libnotify/files

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack pidgin-libnotify-0.14-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./pidgin-libnotify-0.14-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pidgin-libnotify-0.14-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/pidgin-libnotify-0.14-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

